  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Reiuji Clan, Level 8+<br /><strong>Description</strong>: Your radiant chakra allows you to control and create air currents around you. You gain the following Benefits;</p><ul><li>You gain Wind Nature Release Affinity. You are now able to add jutsu with the corresponding Keyword to your jutsu list. If you already have this nature release, you can learn a wind release jutsu that doesnt count towards your jutsu known limit.</li><li>Weakened counts as an elemental condition for the purposes of the <strong>Swirl</strong> effects of Wind release jutsu.</li><li>When concentrating on a jutsu with the wind release keyword, you gain a flight speed equal to half your movement speed. This becomes equal to your full movement speed when concentrating on two jutsu with the wind release keyword.</li></ul>",
